What is your overall assessment of this course?
Do you expect to use this class for credit toward your major, or toward a pre-professional program?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: THST 210 is gives the student a summary of various acting techniques through text analysis and exercises. Yes, I would recommend this course to another student because it is very interesting.
It's a great introductory course to the major and will help you figure out what types of courses you should take in the future to most help you develop your skills as a performer.
This class is required if you are a THST major, but anyone interested in performance can gain a lot from it.
